 Justification:
 This program, PE 0305114F Mods, P-3A Mod 2, Air Traffic Navigation, Integration and Coordination System (ATNAVICS), is a new start.

 PE 0102412F Joint Surveillance System (JSS), North Warning System (NWS) and Archer within the Atmospheric Early Warning System (AEWS) of systems.
 - FY 2026 will fund technical refresh efforts and procurement of components needed for these systems to maintain required Operational Availability (Ao) and meet lifecycle requirements.

 PE 0102325F Joint Surveillance System (JSS) and North Warning System (NWS) within the Atmospheric Early Warning System (AEWS) of systems
 - FY 2026 will fund technical refresh efforts and procurement of components needed for these systems to maintain required Operational Availability (Ao) and meet lifecycle requirements.

 PE 0305114F Air Traffic Control and Landing Systems (ATCALS) - Low Cost Modifications
 - FY 2026 funds continue ATCALS low cost modifications, to include installation and program support, as prioritized by the program office and the Weapon System Review Executive Committee (WSR-EC).

 PE 0305114F ATCALS - ATNAVICS
 - FY26 funds procure obsolescence and diminishing manufacturing source kits for two systems. Funding includes installation and program support.

 PE 0305137F National Airspace System (NAS) FY 2026 funds:
 - Continue low cost modifications, to include installation and program support, as prioritized by the program office and the WSR-EC.
 - Continue life cycle replacement of obsolete components and mitigation of diminishing manufacturing sources for the Digital Airport Surveillance Radar (DASR), Standard Terminal Automation Replacement
 System (STARS), and integration of Automatic Protocol Exchange (APEX) kits to allow interoperability with host nation automation systems. Funding includes hardware, program support costs, and installation
 when required - reference the P-3a exhibit for details.




